// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1540 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4df9c96a-413f-5e2a-8511-596eedc23095

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:10* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:9*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
